      "message": "Hmm.  This is intended mostly as a stop-gap feature for internal developers, so that we can compare emulator tracking with ground-truth, not a fully-fledged feature.  Ideally we would plumb this through the sensor stack as a POSE_6DOF: https://developer.android.com/reference/kotlin/android/hardware/Sensor#type_pose_6dof\n\nFor automation support, this is very good feedback though-- I\u0027ll keep that in mind.  We\u0027re already logging out a protobuf instead of a string, but we should definitely try to buffer it in memory and do flushes on another thread.",
